ne, ultrasound) effectively anchor the commentary"], "weaknesses": ["Explanations remain general and repetitive, with little distinction between the objects\u00e2\u0080\u0099 contributions", "Analysis rarely engages core TOK concepts (ways of knowing, knowledge communities, ethical dimensions)", "Very limited external evidence or citations\u00e2\u0080\u0094arguments rest largely on assertion and anecdote", "Commentary sometimes drifts into descriptive detail rather than exploring knowledge issues in depth"], "calculationMethod": "Holistic AI evaluation: The exhibition fulfills the requirements for band 5\u00e2\u0080\u00936: it identifies three specific objects, situates them in real-world contexts, and maintains a clear focus on the prompt \u00e2\u0080\u009cWhy do we seek knowledge?\u00e2\u0080\u009d. Each object is defended with a recognisable, if basic, justification. However, the work falls short of higher bands because its links to the prompt are often surface-level and repetitive, it lacks rigorous engagement with TOK terminology and concepts, and it offers minimal supporting evidence. These limitations anchor the performance at the lower end of the 5\u00e2\u0080\u00936 band, warranting a final score of 5.", "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}], "strandSelections": [{"versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "strandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "selectedBandId": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "bandScore": 5, "reasoning": "$49"}], "annotations": [{"id": "647195ad-f308-4a40-b41a-8206bd84b54a", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.1189, "y": 0.0886, "width": 0.7666, "height": 0.08240000000000001}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1189, "y": 0.0886}, {"x": 0.8855, "y": 0.0886}, {"x": 0.8855, "y": 0.171}, {"x": 0.1189, "y": 0.171}], "comment": "This discussion of non-invasive knowledge is descriptive. To deepen, connect to TOK concepts like reliability and ethics in technological knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "969d6927-f358-45b2-abe1-10c90e009ba0", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.1226, "y": 0.2186, "width": 0.7597999999999999, "height": 0.21330000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1226, "y": 0.2186}, {"x": 0.8824, "y": 0.2186}, {"x": 0.8824, "y": 0.4319}, {"x": 0.1226, "y": 0.4319}], "comment": "The idea of transforming uncertainty into informed assumptions is compelling but needs TOK vocabulary (e.g., justification, evidence) and concrete examples to support your argument.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "774caaca-0c33-43ee-998e-09d77fb9c4b6", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.0877, "width": 0.7541, "height": 0.11710000000000001}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.0877}, {"x": 0.8786, "y": 0.0877}, {"x": 0.8786, "y": 0.2048}, {"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.2048}], "comment": "This commentary describes the microscope\u00e2\u0080\u0099s function but remains at a descriptive level. Strengthen your analysis by linking to specific ways of knowing (e.g., sense perception, reason) and how they shape medical knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "00c5e114-3300-41fe-a082-cd73e61d0d29", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.117, "y": 0.2329, "width": 0.7704, "height": 0.1487}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.117, "y": 0.2329}, {"x": 0.8874, "y": 0.2329}, {"x": 0.8874, "y": 0.3816}, {"x": 0.117, "y": 0.3816}], "comment": "The discussion of unveiling the invisible repeats earlier points without adding new insight. To advance, explore a distinct TOK issue such as the role of technologies in mediating knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "c33c1123-15ac-4a3a-9e40-4e190a0e538b", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.117, "y": 0.1518, "width": 0.7717, "height": 0.2151}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.117, "y": 0.1518}, {"x": 0.8887, "y": 0.1518}, {"x": 0.8887, "y": 0.3669}, {"x": 0.117, "y": 0.3669}], "comment": "This paragraph offers descriptive context but does not critically explore how \u00e2\u0080\u0098seeking knowledge\u00e2\u0080\u0099 manifests as a TOK theme. To improve, connect examples (hunting, farming) to knowledge issues such as justification or certainty.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "bcdf17f3-7b27-4d39-9856-19143bcc5706", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.2686, "y": 0.48, "width": 0.45280000000000004, "height": 0.42780000000000007}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.2686, "y": 0.48}, {"x": 0.7214, "y": 0.48}, {"x": 0.7214, "y": 0.9078}, {"x": 0.2686, "y": 0.9078}], "comment": "The photograph of the microscope is a strong, concrete real-world object that anchors your exploration of the prompt in a tangible context, fulfilling the requirement for specific object selection.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "7ac1979c-e177-46b7-b5f4-2479f9e9db1f", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.3755, "y": 0.0868, "width": 0.24210000000000004, "height": 0.019199999999999995}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.3755, "y": 0.0868}, {"x": 0.6176, "y": 0.0868}, {"x": 0.6176, "y": 0.106}, {"x": 0.3755, "y": 0.106}], "comment": "The introduction frames seeking knowledge in broad terms but lacks engagement with specific TOK concepts (e.g., ways of knowing or knowledge questions). Consider introducing precise TOK terminology to ground your exploration.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "43b8fefc-a0ff-49bf-90e4-f3af6c763ba9", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.4096, "width": 0.7579, "height": 0.18209999999999998}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.4096}, {"x": 0.8824, "y": 0.4096}, {"x": 0.8824, "y": 0.5917}, {"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.5917}], "comment": "The claim that knowledge reduces pain and extends life is asserted but lacks supporting evidence or references. Incorporate specific examples or data to substantiate this justification.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "85768b6e-5cd8-416b-a8f0-400d3f9293d3", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.7898, "width": 0.7642, "height": 0.11710000000000009}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.7898}, {"x": 0.8887, "y": 0.7898}, {"x": 0.8887, "y": 0.9069}, {"x": 0.1245, "y": 0.9069}], "comment": "The passage notes insight into ancient culture but lacks specific examples of how scholars used the inscriptions. Include a detailed case (e.g., Champollion\u00e2\u0080\u0099s methods) to support your justification.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "64fdf657-4f2a-4833-a53a-839465048ddb", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1239, "y": 0.3108, "width": 0.7585, "height": 0.05209999999999998}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1239, "y": 0.3108}, {"x": 0.8824, "y": 0.3108}, {"x": 0.8824, "y": 0.3629}, {"x": 0.1239, "y": 0.3629}], "comment": "The personal anecdote adds colour but is largely narrative. Strengthen the link to the IA prompt by analysing how that encounter shaped your understanding of knowledge production.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "36e96fa4-3873-4f7d-9d33-46ab1dc360ed", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1358, "y": 0.3776, "width": 0.7309, "height": 0.0832}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1358, "y": 0.3776}, {"x": 0.8667, "y": 0.3776}, {"x": 0.8667, "y": 0.4608}, {"x": 0.1358, "y": 0.4608}], "comment": "The metaphor of \u00e2\u0080\u0098doors opened\u00e2\u0080\u0099 is evocative but abstract. Ground this in TOK by discussing specific knowledge claims or shared knowledge structures revealed by the Rosetta Stone.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "10276f1a-c86b-4a77-9c7f-5cca8981a884", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.3937, "y": 0.4457, "width": 0.20380000000000004, "height": 0.020000000000000018}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.3937, "y": 0.4457}, {"x": 0.5975, "y": 0.4457}, {"x": 0.5975, "y": 0.4657}, {"x": 0.3937, "y": 0.4657}], "comment": "The label \u00e2\u0080\u009cMy Uncle\u00e2\u0080\u0099s Microscope\u00e2\u0080\u009d names the object but could be enhanced by briefly stating the precise context (e.g., used in clinical diagnosis) to clarify its TOK significance.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "13e3946e-3591-4f41-bfca-592cb1645c34", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1176, "y": 0.7827, "width": 0.7697999999999999, "height": 0.08420000000000005}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1176, "y": 0.7827}, {"x": 0.8874, "y": 0.7827}, {"x": 0.8874, "y": 0.8669}, {"x": 0.1176, "y": 0.8669}], "comment": "This sentence trails off and lacks clarity. Ensure each point is fully articulated and connected back to the IA prompt to maintain precision and coherence.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "f0dddd8d-f508-4b1c-8f62-a5431585b7ce", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1277, "y": 0.0868, "width": 0.749, "height": 0.052099999999999994}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1277, "y": 0.0868}, {"x": 0.8767, "y": 0.0868}, {"x": 0.8767, "y": 0.1389}, {"x": 0.1277, "y": 0.1389}], "comment": "The Rosetta Stone is introduced effectively, but the link to the prompt remains general. To deepen, analyse how decipherment exemplifies collaboration across knowledge communities.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "3394b13d-b948-4bb3-9007-f7f7ac8f7e9e", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.2925, "y": 0.3958, "width": 0.40249999999999997, "height": 0.36200000000000004}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.2925, "y": 0.3958}, {"x": 0.695, "y": 0.3958}, {"x": 0.695, "y": 0.7578}, {"x": 0.2925, "y": 0.7578}], "comment": "The image of the Rosetta Stone is a compelling real-world object that vividly illustrates a key epistemic breakthrough, effectively anchoring your exhibition in concrete history.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "f9271921-b58c-45b0-9c95-269aff18bb23", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.117, "y": 0.0877, "width": 0.7736, "height": 0.1501}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.117, "y": 0.0877}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.0877}, {"x": 0.8906, "y": 0.2378}, {"x": 0.117, "y": 0.2378}], "comment": "This explanation describes the stele\u00e2\u0080\u0099s features but misses an opportunity to discuss knowledge frameworks (e.g., scope and applications) that TOK explores.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "8530f788-9973-4d79-8b6d-ab264f7160f2", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1208, "y": 0.5218, "width": 0.7646999999999999, "height": 0.1492}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1208, "y": 0.5218}, {"x": 0.8855, "y": 0.5218}, {"x": 0.8855, "y": 0.671}, {"x": 0.1208, "y": 0.671}], "comment": "The claim about transcending cultural barriers could be enriched by referencing TOK ideas of perspective and bias, showing how context influences understanding.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "67749cd4-6225-432b-896c-03623dea97e8", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 5, "bbox": {"x": 0.1208, "y": 0.1879, "width": 0.7596999999999999, "height": 0.44969999999999993}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1208, "y": 0.1879}, {"x": 0.8805, "y": 0.1879}, {"x": 0.8805, "y": 0.6376}, {"x": 0.1208, "y": 0.6376}], "comment": "The ultrasound images are well described technically but lack explicit connection to the IA prompt. Discuss how medical imaging challenges assumptions about certainty and observation.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "0211bf2b-1794-43fc-83f0-ac4b0f36d72c", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.117, "y": 0.7177, "width": 0.7717, "height": 0.11619999999999997}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.117, "y": 0.7177}, {"x": 0.8887, "y": 0.7177}, {"x": 0.8887, "y": 0.8339}, {"x": 0.117, "y": 0.8339}], "comment": "The conclusion about the Rosetta Stone\u00e2\u0080\u0099s testament to human pursuit is broad. Refine by linking to concrete knowledge questions or ethical implications of knowledge transmission.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "6d28c108-f8bb-40ee-8535-9147aaf9481e", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 5, "bbox": {"x": 0.1277, "y": 0.7217, "width": 0.7509, "height": 0.08419999999999994}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1277, "y": 0.7217}, {"x": 0.8786, "y": 0.7217}, {"x": 0.8786, "y": 0.8059}, {"x": 0.1277, "y": 0.8059}], "comment": "The paragraph introduces the ultrasound\u00e2\u0080\u0099s symbolic power effectively, illustrating the fusion of science and human curiosity as a real-world manifestation of the prompt.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "8082dda4-03fb-4617-9920-0e2c89e0418e", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": null, "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.1157, "y": 0.5116, "width": 0.151, "height": 0.017299999999999982}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1157, "y": 0.5116}, {"x": 0.2667, "y": 0.5116}, {"x": 0.2667, "y": 0.5289}, {"x": 0.1157, "y": 0.5289}], "comment": "Including the word count here is an administrative detail; consider removing it to maintain focus on your analysis.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": null}, {"id": "06fcc5eb-28a8-4cca-8abd-3ec0a61b2c7f", "versionId": "69c0915a-6838-4dff-b6b0-29977dffb690", "criterionId": null, "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 6, "bbox": {"x": 0.1157, "y": 0.5766, "width": 0.1271, "height": 0.019100000000000006}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1157, "y": 0.5766}, {"x": 0.2428, "y": 0.5766}, {"x": 0.2428, "y": 0.5957}, {"x": 0.1157, "y": 0.5957}], "comment": "The bibliography contains only one entry. Expand your sources to include academic articles or TOK references to strengthen your evidence base.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": null}]}]}}, "rubricData": {"id": 57, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "version": 1, "status": "published", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:43.512632+00", "totalMarks": 10, "description": null, "type": "TOK", "rubricSpecificInfo": null, "tags": [""], "isArchived": false, "gradeBoundaryId": "52ad2701-27bc-42f3-be3f-d63b98d98139", "name": "TOK Exhibition", "slug": "tok-exhibition", "rubricCriteria": [{"id": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "revisionId": 57, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition", "label": null, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:55.358727+00", "updatedAt": "2025-07-16 11:21:18.828885+00", "isGradable": true, "showGradedScore": true, "isChecklistCriterion": false, "description": null, "rubricCriterionBands": [{"id": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 0, "marksTo": 0, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:46.486581+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f7cb0652-0737-403e-8f65-be13bd2fd7f1", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "content": "The exhibition does not reach the standard described by the other levels or does not use one of the IA prompts provided.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:58.577216+00"}]}, {"id": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 1, "marksTo": 2, "orderIndex": 1, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:47.076074+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "861f06ce-2b51-46ce-a6ee-3022e7080288", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "content": "The exhibition presents\nthree objects, but the\nreal-world contexts of\nthese objects are not\nstated, or the images\npresented may be\nhighly generic images of\ntypes of object rather\nthan of specific\nreal-world objects. Links\nbetween the objects\nand the selected IA\nprompt are made, but\nthese are minimal,\ntenuous, or it is not\nclear what the student is\ntrying to convey.\nThere is very little\njustification offered for\nthe inclusion of each\nobject in the exhibition.\nThe commentary on the\nobjects is highly\ndescriptive or consists\nonly of unsupported\nassertions.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:04.443183+00"}]}, {"id": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 3, "marksTo": 4, "orderIndex": 2, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.072006+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "e8acd337-a77d-4319-a744-06094151d57b", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of the objects may be implied rather than explicitly stated. Basic links between the objects and the selected IA prompt are made, but the explanation of these links is unconvincing and/or unfocused. There is a superficial justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Reasons for the inclusion of the objects are offered, but these are not supported by appropriate evidence and/or lack relevance to the selected IA prompt. There may be significant repetition across the justifications of the different objects", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:20.428881+00"}]}, {"id": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 5, "marksTo": 6, "orderIndex": 3, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.868343+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "c257e18a-e3b8-46f4-b3b9-d9ea5cd5db84", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of these objects may be vaguely or imprecisely stated. There is some explanation of the links between the three objects and the selected IA prompt. There is some justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Some of the points are supported by evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:31.312862+00"}]}, {"id": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 7, "marksTo": 8, "orderIndex": 4, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:49.555746+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f16fe76e-abd8-4dc1-9a4f-50ab9e121c99", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects and their real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are explained, although this explanation may lack precision and clarity in parts. There is a justification of the contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. Many of the points are supported by appropriate evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:40.123527+00"}]}, {"id": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 9, "marksTo": 10, "orderIndex": 5, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:50.346899+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "055fe2ad-3ef1-4074-af44-83cc3440cc7a", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "content": "The exhibition clearly identifies three objects and their specific real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are clearly made and well-explained. There is a strong justification of the particular contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. All, or nearly all, of the points are well-supported by appropriate evidence and explicit references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:51.46084+00"}]}], "rubricCriterionStrands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:59.452498+00", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?"}]}]}, "similarExemplars": [{"id": "d1111437-1987-4ff1-b872-66c01db93cdd", "title": "Why do we seek knowledge?", "description": "", "tags": ["grade-C", "tok", "sl"], "slug": "why-do-we-seek-knowledge-2", "isPublic": true, "isPremium": true, "showScores": true, "createdAt": "2025-08-05T08:00:25.428Z", "userSubmissionId": "c29595f7-c016-4513-b728-531f86a45ea8", "submissionId": "55a2123f-3165-4274-9df1-9c87b63a1d1a", "similarity": 0.6133010959999999, "normalizedScore": 0.5, "compositeScore": 0.5793107672, "matchingFileId": "", "matchingChunkId": "", "matchingChunkNumber": 0, "userSubmission": {"id": "c29595f7-c016-4513-b728-531f86a45ea8", "score": "C", "scoreType": "letter", "level": null, "researchQuestion": null, "tokPrompt": null, "title": "Why do we seek knowledge?", "cohort": "M25", "createdAt": "2025-07-15T17:00:22.531Z", "subjectId": 582, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "subject": {"id": 582, "title": "Theory of Knowledge (TOK)", "slug": "ib-theory-of-knowledge-tok"}, "rubric": {"id": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "title": "TOK Exhibition", "type": "TOK"}, "totalRawMark": 6, "totalModeratedMark": 5}, "submission": {"id": "55a2123f-3165-4274-9df1-9c87b63a1d1a", "type": "TOK", "level": "SL", "createdAt": "2025-08-05T07:58:14.776Z", "files": [{"submissionId": "55a2123f-3165-4274-9df1-9c87b63a1d1a", "id": "476bbc73-c5f3-4f0a-ab6b-2f7795bf0165", "fileUrl": "https://grader-public.revisiondojo.com/exemplars/1754380698828_Why_do_we_seek_knowledge.application_pdf", "fileName": "Why_do_we_seek_knowledge.application/pdf", "fileType": "application/pdf", "thumbnailUrl": "https://grader-public.revisiondojo.com/thumbnail/476bbc73-c5f3-4f0a-ab6b-2f7795bf0165.png", "pageCount": 6, "versionId": "4e1beb25-efe9-43ff-9f33-a6543c24e969", "versionNumber